doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    title Home
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.2.1/css/bulma.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.6.3/css/font-awesome.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/style.css')
    link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oswald")
  body
    // Header
    include header

    // Content
    .home-section
      // Hero content: will be in the middle
      .hero-body
        .home-section-bg
        .container.has-text-centered
          h1.title
            | RIDE WITH ME
          h2.subtitle
            | We are buses, where you can pick your own bus stop.


    .container.main-container
      .content
        h2.intro-h2.text-center Hate to get into crowded public transport in the morning?<br>Don't feel like paying heaps of money to Taxi or Uber over and over again?<br><strong>WE ARE YOUR SOLUTION</strong>

    section.section
      .container
        .heading
          h1.title.text-center What you will get from us

      .columns.col-whatget
        .column.text-center
          img(src="img/shield.png", alt="")
          h2 Safety
          p Our drivers will be examined by professionals in government and that's we are safer compare to any other carpooling or  any other similar companies out there.
        .column.text-center
          img(src="img/money.png", alt="")
          h2 Price
          p Our price is fixed based on your distance. This means that you will be able to manage your finance more accurately as you will only need to pay us once a week or month and we will make sure you reach your desired destination everytime!
        .column.text-center
          img(src="img/dancing.png", alt="")
          h2 FUN!
          p We will matched driver interest with passenger interest so that the atmosphere in the car will always be your favorite no matter you like it to be quiet or crazy!

    section.section.section-howitwork
      .container
        .heading
          h1.title.text-center How it works

      .columns.col-howitwork
        .column
          img(src="img/home-psg.jpg", alt="")
        .column
          .content
            h2.text-color For Passengers
            p Simply give us your personal detail and we will fetch you FROM YOUR HOUSE TO YOUR DESIRED DESTINATION ON A WEEKLY OR MONTHLY BASIS JUST LIKE A SCHOOL BUS.
            p Give us your personal details such as your residential address and desired destination (Such as your school or office), time you need to arrive your office and time you need to leave your office.
            p We will then fetch you and about 1-2 more customers and make sure you guys reach your office on time!

      .columns.col-howitwork
        .column
          .content
            h2.text-color For Drivers
            p We offer fixed pay. Any other driver in similar industry will have their pay strongly depends on the luck that day. However, we can ensure you to have a fixed income as we aim to maintain long term relationship with all the passengers that come to us.
            p Also, you will not have to concern about your current job as you will know when you have to pick the customer up beforehand. This means that this is your best opportunity to earn EXTRA INCOME!
        .column
          img(src="img/home-driver.jpg", alt="")

    section.section.section-register
      .container
        .heading
          h1.title.text-center Join Us. It's FREE.

        .columns.register-col
          .column.text-center
            img(src="img/car.png", alt="")
            a.button.is-large I am Driver.
            p I drive to work place every day.
          .column.text-center
            img(src="img/psg.png", alt="")
            a.button.is-large I am Passenger.
            p I am looking for a ride.


    include footer